  "pnpm version:check && pnpm changelog:pm:check && pnpm contracts:check && pnpm security:scan && pnpm quality:static && npm pack --dry-run",null,project,240,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null
close_reason: Resolved CI contracts snapshot temp cleanup ENOTEMPTY failure
